<lb n="0021b13"/><head type="no">No. 1038 [No. 1037]</head>
<lb n="0021b14"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0021021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】平安時代寫東寺三密藏本</note>清淨觀世<note n="0021022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＋（菩薩）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0021022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">音＋（菩薩）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0021022"><lem>音</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">音菩薩</rdg></app>普賢陀羅尼<note n="0021023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【甲】</note><app n="0021023"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">經一卷</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0021b15"/>
<lb n="0021b16"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0021024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大〕－【明】</note><app n="0021024"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>唐總持<note n="0021025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔寺〕－【宋】</note><app n="0021025"><lem>寺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>沙門<note n="0021026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔釋〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0021026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔釋〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0021026"><lem>釋</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>智通譯</byline>
<lb n="0021b17"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時婆伽婆。在王舍城耆闍崛
<lb n="0021b18"/><note n="0021027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">山＋（中）【三】</note><note n="0021027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">山＋（中）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0021027"><lem>山</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">山中</rdg></app>。與大比丘眾五百人俱。菩薩無央數。爾
<lb n="0021b19"/>時觀世音菩薩。與九十二俱<note n="0021028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">胝＝知【甲】</note><app n="0021028"><lem>胝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>菩薩同座。時
<lb n="0021b20"/>觀世音菩薩。於晨朝<note n="0021029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（時）＋從【三】</note><note n="0021029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（時）＋從【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0021029"><lem>從</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">時從</rdg></app>坐而起。整衣服合
<lb n="0021b21"/>掌恭敬。頭面禮佛而白佛言。世尊我欲說普
<lb n="0021b22"/>賢陀羅尼。為憐愍利益一切眾生故。我從過
<lb n="0021b23"/>去月光佛所受得此&CB00057;。今欲對佛說此陀羅
<lb n="0021b24"/>尼。唯願世尊聽我說之。即說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0021b25"/><p type="dharani">那謨<note n="0021030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔遏〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0021030" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>〔遏〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0021030"><lem>遏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>羅<note place="inline"><note n="0021031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】下同</note><app n="0021031"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg></app></note>怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>跢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜耶<note place="inline">一</note><note n="0021032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＋（上）夾註【宋】【元】【甲】，（上聲）【明】</note><app n="0021032"><lem>那</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">那<note place="inline">上</note></rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">那上聲</rdg></app>謨
<lb n="0021b26"/>阿<note n="0021033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＝&CB00074;【三】【甲】</note><note n="0021033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利＝&CB00074;【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0021033"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00074;</rdg></app>耶婆路枳羝攝皤<note place="inline"><note n="0021034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（上）＋二【宋】【元】【甲】＊，（上聲）＋二【明】＊</note><app n="0021034"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">上二</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">上聲二</rdg></app>合</note>羅<note place="inline"><note n="0021035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】下同</note><app n="0021035"><lem>去</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">去聲</rdg></app></note>耶<note place="inline">二</note><note n="0021036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">菩＋（去）【宋】【元】，（去聲）【明】</note><app n="0021036"><lem>菩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">菩去</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">菩去聲</rdg></app>提
